==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tong
<hw>Tong</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Chinese
<ets>t'ang</ets>, lit., hall.]</ety> <def>In China, an association,
secret society, or organization of any kind; in the United States,
usually, a secret association of Chinese such as that of the
highbinders; in the U. S. the <ex>tongs</ex> have been frequently
associated with criminal activity and gang warfare.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

